Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小尋啊  我是媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我40秒後到家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年  你臉色蒼白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是好事…當然是好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼解釋這倆傢伙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「是她倆硬要住在這裡的」這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽真的會相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我對少年你沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄個不好就可能被貼上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「父母不在期間帶女生回家」的標籤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣盯著會懷孕的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭～討厭～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這不公正的對待表示抗議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧  宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們又擅自闖進來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  大白天的就好大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再激烈點！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}少年  你居然敢襲擊奈亞子  膽子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽…哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是你想像中的那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一直微笑著潛行在您兒子身邊的混沌——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞拉托提普
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞拉托提普？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了懷上真尋的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未來…更正  是從星之國度千里迢迢而來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把我當成兒媳婦  叫我奈亞子就行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒媳婦你個頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的媽媽  初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奈亞子的妻子克圖格亞  可以叫我克子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子你個頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親自生孩子或者讓你生都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子裡裝的是花園牧場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛行的混沌和克圖格亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她當時隨口亂扯的話竟會真的成為伏線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}這傲嬌和叉子PLAY都是源於\N曾記載在禁忌黑之書中的被詛咒的邪神獵人的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真尋身上也留有這種血！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我也沒想到會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小尋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊離開她倆身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…慢著媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然會在自己家裡遇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我們呢…非但沒襲擊您兒子…而且還救過他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎  小尋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  不是的…這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子好像人畜無害的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看它的眼神就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…夏塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比你的主人我先得到母親大人的寵愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的寵物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是  而且擁有一雙可愛眼睛的我  別說人畜無害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擔任著真尋的護衛一職
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小尋的護衛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我詳細說下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要爆發全面戰爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此回必將其徹徹底底剝奪殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3c7A2BE3\shad0\fscx75\bord6}Mother's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3cFFFFFF\shad0\fscx75}Mother's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星保護機構
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的娛樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大致上明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這母子的擁抱到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在補充釨元素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釨元素？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以輪到媽媽來說明一下狀況了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊  媽媽在做邪神獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？邪神獵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打獵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編寫這本書的就是媽媽大學時代研究會的教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  媽媽受到這位教授的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾幫助他一起狩獵邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是爸爸知道這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  夫妻之間沒有什麼可隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然包容妻子打零工  真是體貼的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也正是喜歡他這點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的父母  好恩愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(331,323)\fs20}lovelove
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來恩愛一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話  love後面會跟著克拉夫特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：克蘇魯神話作者洛夫克拉夫特的梗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  和我來親親愛愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓即將誕生的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承我們的裝備與能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我死了你都別想！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢         
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}放開我  克子  隨便去找個夜魘交尾去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我想和奈亞子交尾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}給我差不多一點啊  你這個變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}和奈亞子在一起  疼痛都讓我感覺好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你還有氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真是個難纏的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一起回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  爸爸這次也是很勉強才獲得了假期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了彌補  這段時間估計會住在公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是邪神獵人  但也沒有做很危險的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一份零工而已  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是份零工啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是我太武斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡…完全沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真是好孩子呢  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始出發捕獲目標人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的霸權  終將落入我們的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為也許還會有敵人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會繼續保護真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的工作是不是該到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…我們還有保護地球幻夢境的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能繼續將此處作為據點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  媽媽  肯定不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  留她倆在這兒也沒什麼大問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼輕易地決定真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她倆不止眼神  各方面來講都很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們在保護地球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定得幫助她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是母親大人  真明白事理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說我正式成為八坂家的新娘了  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  奈亞子喜歡小尋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES！我無比認真地深愛著真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果是作為「新娘」  就有點無法認同了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我希望小尋能過更普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和奈亞子結為戀人或夫妻這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該更慎重的考慮一下  就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是借宿很歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也要和小尋一直做朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAN值正在持續下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來進入期待已久的禮物時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次的禮品是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又買這些老式的遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊  買這些東西時會有種為逝去的美好記憶買單的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡打遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們會很談得來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要趕緊玩玩看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  媽媽肚子也餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃小尋做的晚飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想吃哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大份的釨元素哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我多放蔬菜大蒜和油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  該做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你也在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得烹飪時共同作業會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古話說的好  奇跡總會在邂逅到最棒的搭檔時觸發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不想讓你進廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼絕情的言詞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道你會用什麼材料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確至今為止也許是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(274,323)\fs20}邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是「人」是會長進的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那給我解釋一下你手裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是宇宙知名品牌的肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎布·尼古拉絲牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：莎布·尼古拉絲為克蘇魯神話中的外神之一\N其形象為黑雲般的巨大肉塊  有著許多觸手  以及滴著黏液的大嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孕育千萬子孫的森之黑山羊 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：出自洛夫克拉夫特  《暗夜呢喃》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑  我剛才應該全扔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想為你和母親大人獻上一餐美味的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你的食材僅限地球產
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激萬分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子定當竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂週年慶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  克子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和母親大人在討論遊戲經
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  宇宙也有遊戲機的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  X-oth和HS3平分市場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是覺得地球的遊戲機比較受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  我丟個音爆彈咯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是真尋  真有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「YES·NO抱枕」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管放馬過來吧  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦討厭啦  這也是喜歡的一種表現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果兩邊都是YES啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了隨時接受真尋的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又軟又滑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆給我收斂點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨間釨元素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你們倆  不可以打架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不給我收手  當心我揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍人得做好挨揍的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰翻別人可不是什麼難事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過不可以打架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人！請冷靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是乖孩子！沒有打架！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  我先走了  前面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為媽媽回來  就可以回到過去的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似情況更糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？站得起來不？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  有沒有哪疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒摔倒  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  我也在想心事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那互相扯平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦  是個善良的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善良的大哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不後悔嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己選擇的道路  義無反顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在大庭廣眾之下犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  早上起就累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來才知道八坂同學有兩個同齡的親戚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非還有其他不認識的親戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  後來和八坂怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿  沒有進展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼靦腆的真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會冷不防地推倒我  向造孩子發展…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠緒  有沒有讓奈亞子整晚淫慾肆意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱血沸騰的作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…珠緒  怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  男友攻陷法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…這個怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力擠  強調胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一陣惡寒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  午飯吃熱狗怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說看這東西的正式名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廷達洛斯之獵犬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去時間的稜角裡一頭撞死啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也擅長做三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且問你一下  究竟是什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄧尼奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用勉強裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人說的釨元素到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似地球上的元素週期表沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個媽媽隨口扯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號稱缺乏它會倍感寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了克子  你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月的少年blood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？也給我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年blood？好像休刊了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大概第7期的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的出版社買斷了它  讓它復刊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球也常見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本以外的地區暢銷的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超前的遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的道理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球以外  就能暢銷的雜誌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的話已經先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟下我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到又能見面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  原來你在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是根本找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒來過這種店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有點怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  讓你陪我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我也正好肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這裡偶遇！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我和真尋被命運的紅線繫在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  跟蹤我來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得這麼難聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極混沌的中心  在我耳邊低語道「多買點」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然會上贈品的鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子和克子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  蓮太老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：蓮太為暱稱  與哈斯塔同音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來這孩子也是宇宙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯塔…難道是風屬性的最高位的邪神！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老弟…也就是說他是男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和蓮太從宇宙幼稚園時起就一直同校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙小學的時候蓮太還是年級委員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為可以事事加上宇宙二字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公務員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵飯碗  真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是贏家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}明明只是個家裡蹲  靠著關係給當上了公務員  那的確是贏家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太為什麼來地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來是啊  你不是曾在賀年卡上說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在塞萊諾的圖書館做圖書管理員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這賀年卡內容真傳統啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸最近說要我幫他工作的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是才辭了圖書館的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太爸爸在做什麼工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說在找人就是在幫令尊的忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  應該住在這附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我路癡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住址呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戶主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  這家人姓八坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找的人的名字叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  八坂賴子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…我媽媽
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的婚禮已經指日可待了  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪張嘴在說這種胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可愛的嘴唇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給人的第一印象可是糟透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破這種惡劣情況的秘策終於發動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話「偉大的X的陰謀」  Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你閉嘴啦！


